OL,3,CMajority of adults who expect to run
OL,4,Cout of cash in January 'in red by
OL,5,CThursday'
OL,7,FMore than a third (35%) of people
OL,8,Fexpect to run short of cash before the
OL,9,Fend of January, as winter bills and
OL,10,FChristmas spending take their toll, a
OL,11,Fsurvey indicated.
OL,13,FAnd the majority (51%) of those who
OL,14,Fwill run out of money this month
OL,15,Fexpect to have used up all of their
OL,16,Fmonthly income by Thursday (January
OL,17,F15), according to research for money
OL,18,Fplatform Intuit Credit Karma.
