OL,7,FOne in seven (14%) people are planning
OL,8,Fto take out new credit products in
OL,9,FJanuary to cover the shortfall and get
OL,10,Fahead of their expected debt, the
OL,11,Fsurvey suggested.
OL,13,FCredit Karma's platform data indicated
OL,14,Fthat January 8 was the most popular
OL,15,Fday to apply for credit products in
OL,16,F2025.
