OL,4,Cout of cash in January 'in red by
OL,5,CThursday'
OL,7,FEleonore Hajek, head of product for UK
OL,8,Fand Canada at Intuit Credit Karma,
OL,9,Fsaid: "The new year is often when
OL,10,Fpeople take stock of their finances,
OL,11,Fbut for many, that moment of
OL,12,Freflection can quickly turn into
OL,13,Fconcern, especially around mid-January
OL,14,Fwhen the reality of festive spending
OL,15,Fand a longer time between pay cheques
OL,16,Fcatches up with you."
